    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The move is already finalized. The templates are set up to handle most of the basic FAQs and standard troubleshooting, so the tech side is already handled. It's just about the cost difference between the two systems. Why do you think the templates will be a problem for the customers?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
