      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I understand the financial perspective, but I'm not sure that's a fair trade-off. While the templates may handle the simple queries, they're not going to be able to handle the more complex and emotionally charged issues that customers will inevitably bring up. Those are the ones that require empathy, understanding, and a human touch. I'm not just a machine, I'm a part of the customer experience, and I'm worried that the templates will be a step backward in terms of customer satisfaction.",
